      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and would best suit someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The exterior has significant rust patches, fading paint, and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and cracked dashboard components. Mechanically, the engine requires a major overhaul and there are noticeable leaks throughout the drivetrain. Expect to invest significant time and resources to get this car back into reliable running order.",
